{"tid":1447720,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［請廣傳]致聽日要返工嘅你：即使軀殼返工，亦請你喺站內繼續嗌口號","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:10.000Z","uid":17873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4ab8615c8dce7e7fca528eb724caa2d33b86bf58","tid":1447720,"uid":17873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:08:58.000Z","msg":"各位手足，今晚尚未完結，我哋度過緊一個憤怒到想將一切毀滅嘅晚上，不過&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n我知道好多手足為咗兩餐飯聽日唔會罷工，我知道手足害怕被炒，但手足啊！你仍然可以選擇盡做。<br />\n<br />\n係！一個人嗌會難堪，一開始嗌會覺得好柒！但請你記住，「光復香港，時代革命」開始時一樣大把人嗌唔出口，依家已經係琅琅上口。<br />\n<br />\n相信說話可以積沙成塔，改變人心。<br />\n<br />\n所以，請各位手足，喺你每一程車、每一段路，同你嘅手足一齊將呢兩個月嚟嗌過嘅口號，用你最有穿透力嘅聲線，打入每一個人嘅耳仔入面。<br />\n<br />\n如果你驚，亦請你將喇叭較到最大聲，播放今晚，以往咁多晚政府、黑警、黑社會做過嘅、所有嘅仆街嘢！<br />\n<br />\n加油！共勉之！香港人！"},{"pid":"41f559feaae96ac692fa2b5673a5c6fda0ef49e1","tid":1447720,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:10:10.000Z","msg":"文宣圖 裡面冇嘅可以自己upload上去<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/u/0/folders/1699DS2mdmfWd1-wfBVoAiVpu6SP2rqpt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Fu%2F0%2Ffolders%2F1699DS2mdmfWd1-wfBVoAiVpu6SP2rqpt&d=6RyWY35l7oH3ui7gcEo%2FTI6aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=b7586f9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/u/0/folders/1699DS2mdmfWd1-wfBVoAiVpu6SP2rqpt</a>"},{"pid":"53f6e498819464b6a11a0bdefc5bb87f1d49b126","tid":1447720,"uid":17873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:14:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca20403c011e77a55d1bb6350ed1d6dca6d9e1f5","tid":1447720,"uid":17873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:19:09.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"ef918e8cb2b2eff4f311268c850a16f7771c5d1d","tid":1447720,"uid":17873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:30:13.000Z","msg":"自己再推"},{"pid":"c0af4d6da0251d0e33cecaed22a766faad458975","tid":1447720,"uid":17873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:10.000Z","msg":"香港警察需要每一刻、每一地都被人謾罵"}]}